{
  "text": "In this paper, we are concerned with the initial-value problem associated with the generalized periodic Camassa-Holm (\u00b5CH) equation [CITATION_1] \uf8f1 \uf8f4 \uf8f2 \uf8f4 \uf8f3 \u00b5(u t ) \u2212 u xxt = \u22122\u00b5(u)u x + 2u x u xx + uu xxx , t > 0, x \u2208 R, u(0, x) = u 0 (x), x \u2208 R, u(t, x + 1) = u(t, x), t \u2265 0, x \u2208 R,",
  "citation_candidates": [
    "121564141",
